                      <span>2003-04-03</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>This is an amazing book from cover to cover. I wouldn't know where to start giving compliments on it. I've read several books over the years on business, motivation, and leadership. This book is by far one of the top reads. I strongly recommend it to anyone looking to improve themselves as well as those around them.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Lead to succeed-10 great traits of freat leaders</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>2</span>
